**Spirit Touched** | Extra Miscellaneous | Haunted
__Basics__
When a spiritualist selects a player, that player becomes Spirit Touched until the end of the following day.
__Details__
During the night, the spiritualist may select a player. That player will become Spirit Touched and will be added to the Spirit Touched channel.
The spiritualist and the Spirit Touched can speak to each other privately, but the identity of the spiritualist will not be revealed.

__Simplified__
When a spiritualist selects a player, that player becomes Spirit Touched until the end of the following day.
  
__Formalized__
Passive End Day:
  • Conversation Reset
  • Revoke @ThisAttr from @Self
On Death: Conversation Reset

__Card__
The Spirit Touched has been the target of a Spiritualist
